Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:20.24,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Fu Fu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:23.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無論到哪裏 都要在一起
