Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:32.73,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,300)}隱藏不住的曬痕與少女心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個占卜相當準的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子你還真喜歡占卜什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過利子你是天秤座的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣超差而且要注意水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候太準了也難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會要去泳池  要注意水的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在泳池…溺…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佔什麼卜  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的天秤座在吼叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是騙人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是胡扯的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭氣睡覺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿幸運色藍色的衣服運氣會不會好一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運物是玩偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來水會流到千秋那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過玩偶從災難手裏保護了天秤座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  不愧是幸運物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看它彷彿就是吸取大地水分的大樹一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈別感嘆了快點拿東西把水擦乾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個占卜  是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子不能進入泳池！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖…雖然占卜上是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳裝是藍色的至少會好點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  禁止利子接近泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是為了什麼來這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也來泳池了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡  你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱約看到些藍色的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  幸運色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子  和藤岡一起的話可以進入泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡  利子由於某種理由今天可能會溺水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你說不定可以改變這個命運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡  要緊握住利子的手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天運氣超差？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜什麼的真不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希和淳子好像在一起打工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應聘的時候會有面試之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會做些什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介紹興趣  特長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展示自已的長處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂自我PR啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我PR嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長這種啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長的想法可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來練習吧！練習！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來當面試官問問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來面試  確認你適不適合當面試官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼千秋適合當面試官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  夏奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你自我PR
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子自我PR啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點難懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難懂麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再具體點的更簡單易懂的美少女就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍微失禮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺變得簡單易懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單易懂  合格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就合格了啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就交由我來擔當面試官了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  維持美少女的模式進行面試嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這麼說話有點怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不受理來自對方提出的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請自我PR一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常被人說很開朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田小姐比昨天換下的螢光燈還要明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋小姐  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎餅的袋子太堅固了打不開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剪刀就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起面試更不擅長應對美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡先生  今天來訪我家的動機是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  動機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學打電話邀請我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  邀請什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我簡直就像是沒有禮儀的女子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樣子好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不受理來自對方提出的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只給你一個提示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂自我PR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是把自己是怎麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在考慮些什麼傳達出去就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你自我PR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  現在的我滿腦子只想做這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡平常的南夏奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.76,0:10:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽到這句話的話  就一直要演下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:46.79,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}恐怖～～谷  篇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家鬥惡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:51.80,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}恐怖～～沙漠  篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們一起去把太平洋游個遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  下海之前要先做準備運動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嗎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來海邊要事先我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要做心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.12,0:11:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是穿著泳裝麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備地多充分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你說穿了過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  今天吉野在場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她面前穿泳裝太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野說不定注意到了我的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍不換上泳裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天似乎有點感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想讓阿珍來教我游泳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍微休息下就好了  你先游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  你看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會真希和淳子也會過來匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  千秋她們已經去游了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  要塗防曬油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你塗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍滿臉通紅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香到底用了什麼絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要放手  不能放哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  相信我吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆身體  只動腿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋可不會游泳  溺水了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:14:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想讓你們知道大海的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈你是姐姐  做事之前也考慮下後果吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這海參當我道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為阿珍你說不放手的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也要一直做朋友喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  剛才謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你喜歡海參嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你  我和千秋變得要好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你邀請我一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能來海邊真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到最後都不要鬆懈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回去之前都是海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工很快就要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和春香她們一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  炒麵就是要像皮筋一樣有嚼勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這微微的焦味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然咖喱有分歐洲和印度等各種風味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個是速食咖喱包的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵要泡得有些糊了再吃才算賺到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說都很難吃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個說出來就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易來一趟海邊  都被你給糟蹋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都沒食慾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋好像很失落的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算只有一個人失落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也開心不起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋就交給我吧  你們就去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為有你這種人去照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才讓她誤以為這是理所應當的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春香把千秋寵壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  說得過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候就一定要說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋之所以會變得失落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是因為夏奈說得太過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會去理會沒有協調性的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了那麼多次要等大家一起切西瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛都因為我  害得大家都沒怎麼吃東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想現在大家可能餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想負起責任把西瓜切好給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦  千秋  沒有人在生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  反正你就是個好好先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就來玩切西瓜吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊  右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…稍微往左一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這是…又甜又多汁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘著沙子的部分尤其好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  應該是難吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不去理會她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看這曬痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  完美地曬出了泳裝的痕跡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是之前和你們去海邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天之後  我的夏天就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但不能和修一他們去游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡也不能光著身子到處跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時不能在別人面前露出自己的身體了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了羞澀的少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有著恥辱曬痕的男子漢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那個創口貼是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊  是之前返校的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:15.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是去一次校醫室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  我會一輩子珍惜這個創口貼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不會撕掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了就給我撕掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  也就是說你以真的樣子從千秋那裏得到創口貼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你以阿珍的樣子貼著同樣的創口貼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋就有可能會發現你的真實身份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之還是先把創口貼撕下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我已經決定了絕對不會把這個撕下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是千秋會發現你的真實身份的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  來玩黑白棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是玩的話  右手背會被看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼阿珍  要吃餅幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個還是要用手的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創口貼要被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍一直對我擺著拒絕的姿勢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}拒\N絕\N的\N姿\N勢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前去海邊的時候明明關係還那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在已經討厭我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事  阿珍很珍惜千秋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那個手勢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個姿勢一定是像萬歲什麼的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去認真確認友情吧  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把手藏起來的話不是這樣  而是要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友嗎
